  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th Level, you have an unmated efficiency for your agility. </p><p>Your Dexterity and Wisdom scores increase by 2. </p><p>Your maximum for those scores increases by 2. </p><p>Additionally, once per turn if a ranged weapon attack you make, misses a target creature you can treat the miss as a hit. </p><p>Alternatively, if you fail a Dexterity or Wisdom saving throw, you may treat it as a success. <br />You can use each of these effects twice per rest.</p>",
